  {
    "client_msg_id": "5f5a5ca4-8266-4ca6-8a54-056044fc5f46",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hi <@UAVCC2X70>, I definitely don’t mean CPS.  I might have said “closures” (or callbacks, or...) instead of “continuations”.  I don’t know if there’s a name for this technique, so I will provide a (simple) recipe for it rsn...",
